    • Class it.polimi.ingsw.gc28.model.objectives.ObjectivePosition

      class ObjectivePosition extends Objective implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • patternPosition
          ResourcePrimary[] patternPosition
          this generalizes position patterns. It describes the resource that each card must satisfy, from bottom left to top right. for example, for a main diagonal it would be: [RED, RED, RED]
        • positionType
          PositionType positionType
          this attribute stores the getNeighbors() function that generalizes different kinds of positions.
